entry.title: BabyShiB
entry.content:
BabyShib is a 100% decentralized community

experiment, co-sponsored by the Hong Kong

International Foundation, which pays tribute to SHIBand Floki, and strives to create a ten-thousand-foldcoin, which will be listed in the Hong Kong blockchainsector and connected with major mainstream

exchanges in the future.
